== 2015年动画电影 ==
《[[黑猫警长之翡翠之星|黑猫警长之翡翠之星]]》已经于2015年8月7日上映。<ref >{{cite web |url=http://www.1905.com/news/20150626/905428.shtml#p7 |language= |title=《黑猫警长》发布原画手稿 新角色首度曝光 |publisher=1905电影网 |date=2015-06-26 |accessdate= |archive-date=2015-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626123914/http://www.1905.com/news/20150626/905428.shtml#p7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

